title: Elementalist skills missing from the API

comments.author: Dante.1523
comments.body:
I’ve been playing around with the API a little bit and noticed that Meteor Shower was missing from the files I downloaded. After digging around a little bit, I noticed that all of the Elementalist staff skills “4” and “5” were in fact missing.
I wanted to ask if that is on purpose or if there is something that might be done about that.
